com.conorthomason.garageapp

Class SingletonService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.Application
          • com.conorthomason.garageapp.SingletonService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, java.io.Serializable

    public class SingletonService
extends android.app.Application
implements java.io.Serializable
    SingletonService is used to access both the Garage and EmployeeManagement singletons throughout Android. Handles the saving/loading of these data structures also.
